1504
01:46:14,479 --> 01:46:15,359
[SPEAKER_00] I to znači mnogo.

1505
01:46:15,520 --> 01:46:19,439
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, slično tome, zaustavit ćete snimanje i sjesti ćete i reći: O, dobro.

1506
01:46:20,079 --> 01:46:22,560
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, mislim da je to bilo razočaravajuće.

1507
01:46:24,640 --> 01:46:27,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, nikad ne razočaravajuće.

1508
01:46:27,920 --> 01:46:28,319
[SPEAKER_00] Fantastično.

1509
01:46:28,560 --> 01:46:31,760
[SPEAKER_00] U redu, pa gdje ljudi mogu pronaći tebe i tvoje djelo?

1510
01:46:32,000 --> 01:46:35,359
