1511
01:46:35,520 --> 01:46:35,680
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1512
01:46:36,239 --> 01:46:37,760
[SPEAKER_01] Moj je web-mjesto dobar početak.

1513
01:46:37,840 --> 01:46:38,720
[UNKNOWN] Rafa.design.

1514
01:46:39,199 --> 01:46:40,560
[SPEAKER_00] Rafa je Rafa.

1515
01:46:41,279 --> 01:46:43,279
[SPEAKER_00] Design, ostavit ću vam da to shvatite.

1516
01:46:43,520 --> 01:46:45,520
