1529
01:47:12,479 --> 01:47:13,119
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je to bilo prije šest godina.

1530
01:47:13,520 --> 01:47:13,840
[SPEAKER_00] Luda je.

1531
01:47:14,960 --> 01:47:17,279
