1534
01:47:29,439 --> 01:47:32,720
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, mislim da postoji dosta preklapanja s ovim, ali volio sam tu epizodu.

1535
01:47:32,800 --> 01:47:34,319
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo sjajno.

1536
01:47:34,479 --> 01:47:39,039
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam znao da slušate emisiju, a sad znam.

1537
01:47:39,680 --> 01:47:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala.

1538
01:47:40,720 --> 01:47:41,760
[SPEAKER_00] Fina je stvar.

1539
