[SPEAKER_01] To je dobar način da to kažem.

1558
01:49:12,640 --> 01:49:13,600
[SPEAKER_01] Da, nikad nisam razmišljao o tome.

1559
01:49:13,840 --> 01:49:16,079
[SPEAKER_00] U redu, tako da ćemo ovdje sletjeti avionom.

1560
01:49:16,239 --> 01:49:16,720
[SPEAKER_00] Uspjeli smo.

1561
01:49:16,880 --> 01:49:17,439
[SPEAKER_01] Nasvidenje.

1562
01:49:17,600 --> 01:49:17,680
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala.

1563
01:49:18,239 --> 01:49:18,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je bilo zabavno.

1564
01:49:19,199 --> 01:49:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala ti puno.

1565
01:49:22,239 --> 01:49:23,359
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala na slušanju.

1566
01:49:23,439 --> 01:49:25,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj je epizoda uređivao Jonathan Ruiz.

1567
01:49:26,319 --> 01:49:30,000
