1568
01:49:30,159 --> 01:49:30,239
[SPEAKER_01] C.

1569
01:49:30,479 --> 01:49:32,159
[SPEAKER_01] ili objaviti emisiju izravno na launched.

1570
01:49:32,399 --> 01:49:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] FM-u.

1571
01:49:33,199 --> 01:49:41,039
[SPEAKER_01] Zaista bih volio ocjenu ili recenziju u aplikaciji za podcast po vašem izboru, a bilješke o emisiji i još mnogo toga možete pronaći na launchedfm.com

